Subject: [PATCH v3 24/36] platform/x86: intel_scu_ipc: Add function to remove SCU IPC
Date:   Mon, 13 Jan 2020 16:56:11 +0300
Message-Id: <20200113135623.56286-25-mika.westerberg@linux.intel.com>
